  "original_title": "\u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0b95\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b85\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Important announcement by Energy Minister",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Energy Minister Kanjana Wijesekara has said that operations at Sabugaskanda Refinery have started from today (20).",
        "The minister mentioned that currently 100,000 metric tons of crude oil is being unloaded and another 120,000 metric tons of crude oil is expected to arrive next week.",
        "Also, Minister Kanchana Wijesekhara has assured that the aviation fuel stocks are going to be landed tonight and with these two cargoes, Sabugaskanda Refinery will be able to operate at full capacity for 40 days. (a)"
      ],
